        <sect2 id="kynaptic-status" status="review">
            <title id="title-kynaptic-status">Status Bar</title>
            <para>The Status Bar, located at the bottom of the main window, display the progress of
                operations. For example, when starting &appshort; the status of the operation
                for building the dependency tree is displayed.</para>
            <screenshot>
                <mediaobject>
                    <imageobject>
                        <imagedata fileref="figures/status-bar.png" format="PNG"/>
                    </imageobject>
                </mediaobject>
            </screenshot>
        </sect2>
